.@JoeRogan and UFC Champion @SugaSeanMMA discuss how insanely fast Tesla's Model X Plaid is, how the UFC Champ got two speeding tickets because he feels like he's going 60 when he's going 90, and Joe Rogan teaching his 15-year-old daughter how to drive in Ludicrous Mode.

@JoeRogan: "I'm faster in my Plaid than my Porsche, and it makes no sound... It time travels. 0 to 60 in 1.9 seconds for a four-door sedan. It's bonkers. Just wait until he comes out with that little two-door Roadster. That thing will go 0 to 60 in 1.5 or 1.7, and it will handle because all of the weight will be at the bottom because that's where the weight of the battery is. So it's like a phenomenal center of gravity."

@SugaSeanMMA: "How crazy is that Tesla Model X Plaid? ...I got pulled over again in literally the exact same highway, same neighborhood, same cop. Those Xs are insane. Even on the highway, you're going 90, it feels like you are going 60..."

@JoeRogan: "I taught my 15-year-old how to drive in that. It's always on Ludicrous Mode. It's easy to control. That's the difference between that and other high-powered cars. You can drive very slowly in that easily. It's like the perfect car to drive around. For a commuter car, it's the best car ever... You just plug it in at your house. You never have to go to a gas station."

